@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>
        <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> [Insert Date]</p>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to [Bike Store Name] ("Company", "we", "our", "us"). We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website, [Website URL], and purchase our products.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, shipping address, payment details.</li>
                <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Login credentials, purchase history.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> IP address, device type, browser type, and analytics data.</li>
                <li><strong>Cookies and Tracking:</strong> Data collected via cookies to improve user experience.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>To process and fulfill orders.</li>
                <li>To communicate with you regarding orders, promotions, and updates.</li>
                <li>To improve our website and services.</li>
                <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
            <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal information. However, we may share your data with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Third-party service providers for payment processing and shipping.</li>
                <li>Legal authorities if required by law.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>5. Security Measures</h2>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no method is completely secure, and we encourage users to safeguard their login credentials.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>6. Your Rights & Choices</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal information.</li>
                <li>Opt out of marketing communications.</li>
                <li>Manage cookie preferences.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> [Insert Email]</li>
                <li><strong>Phone:</strong> [Insert Phone Number]</li>
                <li><strong>Mailing Address:</strong> [Insert Address]</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
